com.almeros.android.multitouch

Interface RotateGestureDetector.OnRotateGestureListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MapViewRotateGestureDetectorListener, RotateGestureDetector.SimpleOnRotateGestureListener
    Enclosing class:
    RotateGestureDetector

    public static interface RotateGestureDetector.OnRotateGestureListener
    Listener which must be implemented which is used by RotateGestureDetector to perform callbacks to any implementing class which is registered to a RotateGestureDetector via the constructor.
    See Also:
    RotateGestureDetector.SimpleOnRotateGestureListener
